---
title: Double Hearty Beef & Veg Pie with Kumara Mash Top & Garlicky Greens
description: Sometimes only a pie will do. Satisfy that craving for something warm and comforting with this rich, cheesy mash-topped
number. It's just like Nanna used to make (but better!).
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/67ca55f025f33d23e0b3dbda-59176063.jpeg
